PrecisAuthority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT which will amend the CANADA-SASKATCHEWAN CROP INSURANCE AGREEMENT by introducing a supplemental unseeded acreage insurance benefit of $25 per acre payable to producers who were unable to plant crops before the 1999 seeding deadline.
Attachments
precis:
Authority to enter into a SUPPLEMENTARY AGREEMENT which will amend the
CANADA-SASKATCHEWAN CROP INSURANCE AGREEMENT by introducing a supplemental
unseeded acreage insurance benefit of $25 per acre payable to producers
who were unable to plant crops before the 1999 seeding deadline.
